{"word":"G1450 - ἔγγυος - éngyos - eng'-goo-os - Surety","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔγγυος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">éngyos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">eng'-goo-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Surety</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிணையாளியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"a surety"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <b>&#x03B3;&#x03C5;&#x03B9;&#x0342;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;</b> <b>guion</b> (a <i>limb</i>); <i>pledged</i> (as if <i>articulated</i> by a member), that is, a <i>bondsman:</i> - surety.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}